	of vm_allocate.
	(diskfs_S_fsys_init): Likewise.
	* file-get-trans.c (diskfs_S_file_get_translator): Likewise.
	* file-getfh.c (diskfs_S_file_getfh): Likewise.
	* io-read.c (diskfs_S_io_read): Likewise.

